org.intellimate.izou.system.file

Class FilePublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intellimate.izou.util.IzouModule
      • org.intellimate.izou.system.file.FilePublisher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, MainProvider

    public class FilePublisher
extends IzouModule
    FilePublisher that notifies FileSubscriber objects. It is triggered when a file is reloaded. Particularly file subscribers are mapped to ReloadableFile objects. When a reloadable file is reloaded, all file subscribers belonging to it are notified. All file subscribers in general can also be notified.

      • register

        public void register(ReloadableFile reloadableFile,
                     FileSubscriber fileSubscriber,
                     Identification identification)
              throws IllegalIDException
        Registers a FileSubscriber with a ReloadableFile. So when the reloadableFile is reloaded, the fileSubscriber will be notified. Multiple file subscribers can be registered with the same reloadable file.
        Parameters:
        reloadableFile - the reloadable file that should be observed
        fileSubscriber - the fileSubscriber that should be notified when the reloadable file is reloaded
        identification - the Identification of the FileSubscriber
        Throws:
        IllegalIDException - not yet implemented
